Regarding the polite forms of 食べる, I think 食べませ is not used. Native speakers would say 食べてください, or 食べなさい, for example. So I think it should be noted with the asterisk mark. [[User:Tomos|Tomos]] 11:41, 20 Nov 2004 (UTC)

